| **Jest** | v30.3.0 | Node 18+, `using` auto-cleanup for spies, sharding for 
CI, 37% faster with `unrs-resolver` |
| **Playwright** | v1.59.x | Role-based locators, auto-waiting (never 
`waitForTimeout`), trace viewer, project dependencies for auth |

