Found the root cause. In the Dockerfile, the `runner` stage copies 
`node_modules` from the `deps` stage — but `prisma generate` only ran in the 
`build` stage. So the runtime container has `@prisma/client` package files but 
no generated client at `node_modules/.prisma/client/`, causing `PrismaClient` 
to be undefined at seed time.

Minimal fix: copy `node_modules` from the `build` stage (which has the 
generated client) instead of `deps`.
